@MusicRoadmap.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5213

### 1. Diagnostic Health Check
GET {{MusicRoadmap.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Multi-Tenant Login Attempt (Returns Hashed Session Tokens)
POST {{MusicRoadmap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 3. Secure Token Refresh Rotation Exchange
POST {{MusicRoadmap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_RAW_CLIENT_TOKEN_HERE"
}